Dialogue: 0,0:44:37.66,0:44:39.56,CHS,,0,0,0,,我想起來了，就是他\N{\rENG}I remember. That's him.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:50.00,0:44:51.65,CHS,,0,0,0,,對不起\N{\rENG}I'm sorry.
