Dialogue: 0,1:38:03.67,1:38:07.32,CHS,,0,0,0,,你這一輩子都將為這個孩子付出代價\N{\rENG}You're gonna pay for this child for the rest of your life.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:10.37,1:39:12.54,CHS,,0,0,0,,你像條狗\N{\rENG}You're like a dog.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:13.94,1:39:20.03,CHS,,0,0,0,,像一條沒人要的、受盡虐待的狗\N{\rENG}Like one of those unwanted, mistreated dogs.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:21.48,1:39:26.99,CHS,,0,0,0,,你可以踹它們，可它們還是一直回來找你\N{\rENG}You can kick them, but they keep coming back to you.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:27.34,1:39:29.31,CHS,,0,0,0,,以為要是自己怎麼著乖一點…\N{\rENG}Thinking that somehow if they're good...
Dialogue: 0,1:39:29.35,1:39:32.05,CHS,,0,0,0,,你不能再這樣對待我\N{\rENG}You're not doing this again.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:33.27,1:39:34.86,CHS,,0,0,0,,…你就會愛它們\N{\rENG}You'll love them.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:34.89,1:39:37.87,CHS,,0,0,0,,你就是這麼做的，你不能再這樣對待我\N{\rENG}This is what you do. You're not doing this to me.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:40.06,1:39:42.47,CHS,,0,0,0,,這都是你自找的，蕾切爾\N{\rENG}You brought this on yourself, Rachel.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:44.03,1:39:48.14,CHS,,0,0,0,,如果那一個晚上你躲得遠遠的…\N{\rENG}If you had just stayed away that one night...
Dialogue: 0,1:39:50.18,1:39:53.31,CHS,,0,0,0,,沒過來找我們麻煩\N{\rENG}Just left us all alone.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:56.09,1:39:58.42,CHS,,0,0,0,,梅根也是你害的\N{\rENG}You brought this on Megan.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:58.95,1:40:01.97,CHS,,0,0,0,,某種意義上說，你殺了她\N{\rENG}In a way, you killed her.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:04.66,1:40:06.86,CHS,,0,0,0,,但我沒殺\N{\rENG}But I didn't.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:08.44,1:40:10.24,CHS,,0,0,0,,你殺的\N{\rENG}You did.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:28.97,1:40:31.37,CHS,,0,0,0,,你殺了我們婚姻中的我\N{\rENG}You did this to me in our marriage.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:33.03,1:40:36.07,CHS,,0,0,0,,你讓我快他媽的發瘋了\N{\rENG}You made me fucking crazy.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:40.89,1:40:45.55,CHS,,0,0,0,,你知不知道和一個滿腦子糨糊的人結婚是什麼樣的感覺？\N{\rENG}Do you have any idea what it's like to be married to a fucking blur?
Dialogue: 0,1:43:33.15,1:43:35.14,CHS,,0,0,0,,我沒別的選擇，他…\N{\rENG}I had no choice. He was...
Dialogue: 0,1:43:36.41,1:43:38.41,CHS,,0,0,0,,他會殺了我的\N{\rENG}He would have killed me.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:40.15,1:43:42.93,CHS,,0,0,0,,我也不想傷害他\N{\rENG}I never wanted to hurt him.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:47.58,1:43:49.48,CHS,,0,0,0,,這是正當防衛\N{\rENG}It was self-defense.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:54.60,1:43:56.40,CHS,,0,0,0,,她沒別的選擇\N{\rENG}She had no choice.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:57.20,1:43:59.19,CHS,,0,0,0,,湯姆會殺了她的\N{\rENG}Tom would have killed her.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:01.23,1:44:03.59,CHS,,0,0,0,,整個過程我都看見了\N{\rENG}I saw the whole thing.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:07.41,1:44:09.61,CHS,,0,0,0,,蕾切爾說梅根的事是對的\N{\rENG}Rachel was right about Megan.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:11.74,1:44:14.34,CHS,,0,0,0,,她說的所有事都是對的\N{\rENG}She was right about everything.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:59.10,1:45:02.40,CHS,,0,0,0,,{\i1}現在我們永遠扯平了，我們三個人{\i0}\N{\rENG\i1}We are tied forever now, the three of us.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:05.84,1:45:09.11,CHS,,0,0,0,,{\i1}被我們共同的故事永遠綁在了一起{\i0}\N{\rENG\i1}Bound forever by the story we share.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:42.86,1:45:47.37,CHS,,0,0,0,,{\i1}今天，我坐在另一節車廂裏，我抬頭看向前方{\i0}\N{\rENG\i1}Today, I sit in a different car. And I look ahead.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:48.20,1:45:49.92,CHS,,0,0,0,,{\i1}一切皆有可能{\i0}\N{\rENG\i1}Anything is possible.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:50.46,1:45:54.18,CHS,,0,0,0,,{\i1}因為我不再是從前的那個女孩{\i0}\N{\rENG\i1}Because I am not the girl I used to be.


